\c 135
\s Rwiyo rwokurumbidza Jehovha, iye oga Mwari wazvokwadi
\p
\v 1 Hareruya! Rumbidzai zita raJehovha; Murumbidzei, imwi varanda vaJehovha;
\v 2 imwi mumire mumba maJehovha, Muvazhe dzeimba yaMwari wedu.
\v 3 Rumbidzai Jehovha; nekuti Jehovha akanaka; Imbirai zita rake nziyo dzokurumbidza; nekuti ndizvo zvinofadza.
\v 4 nekuti Jehovha akazvisanangurira Jakobho, NaIsiraeri kuti ave fuma yake chaiyo.
\v 5 nekuti ndinoziva kuti Jehovha . mukuru, Uye kuti Ishe wedu ari kumusoro kwavamwari vose.
\v 6 Zvose zvaakada kuita Jehovha akazviita, Kudenga napasi, nomumakungwa napakadzika pose.
\v 7 Anokwidza makore pamigumo yapasi; Anoita mheni kuuyisa mvura; Anobudisa mhepo panovigwa fuma yake.
\v 8 Ndiye akaparadza matangwe Avanhu neezvipfuwo.
\v 9 Akatuma zviratidzo nezvishamiso mukati mako, iwe Egipita, Pamusoro paFarao napamusoro pavaranda vake vose.
\v 10 Ndiye akaparadza ndudzi zhinji, Nokuuraya madzimambo anesimba.
\v 11 Sihoni mambo wavaAmori, NaOgi mambo weBhashani, Noushe hwose bweKanani;
\v 12 Akapa nyika yavo ive nhaka, Ive nhaka yaIsiraeri vanhu vake.
\v 13 Zita renyu, Jehovha, riripo nokusingaperi; Munorangarirwa Jehovha, kusvikira kumarudzi namarudzi.
\v 14 nekuti Jehovha achatonga vanhu vake, Nokuzvidemba pamusoro pavaranda vake.
\v 15 Zvifananidzo zvavahedheni isirivha nendarama, Mubato wamaoko avanhu.
\v 16 Zvinemiromo, asi hazvitauri; Nameso zvinawo, asi hazvioni;
\v 17 Zvinenzeve, asi hazvinzwi; Hakuna kufema pamiromo yazvo.
\v 18 Vanozviita vachafanana nazvo; Zvirokwazvo, navose vanovimba nazvo.
\v 19 imwi veimba yalsiraeri, rumbidzai Jehovha; imwi veimba yaAroni, rumbidzai Jehovha;
\v 20 imwi veimba yaRevhi, rumbidzai Jehovha; imwi vanotya Jehovha, rumbidzai Jehovha.
\v 21 Jehovha ngaarumbidzwe paZiyoni, Iye agere Jerusaremu. Hareruya!
